                <h1>CDS founding director publishes poetry collection</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e5847084-a656-44d5-9d8e-2932858ec791.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="CDS&#x20;founding&#x20;director&#x20;Iris&#x20;Tillman&#x20;read&#x20;from&#x20;her&#x20;recent&#x20;poetry&#x20;collection&#x20;&quot;All&#x20;This&#x20;Happened&#x20;Long&#x20;Ago&#x20;&#x2013;&#x20;It&#x20;Happens&#x20;Now&quot;&#x20;Sept.&#x20;5.&#x20;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            CDS founding director Iris Tillman read from her recent poetry collection "All This Happened Long Ago – It Happens Now" Sept. 5. 

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/courtesy-of-center-for-documentary-studies-5b8f70ac0fb03">Courtesy of Center for Documentary Studies </a> |
